/me hides
I have however discovered the way to get lots of "free" PAC points.
Although to do so does, in the long run, lose money. And takes roughly a bloody day. :P
02XD
25 cent roulette + bet on red and black + keep hitting the "Spin/Rebet" button.
You will - on most spins - neither win nor lose anything.
(Duh... you lose one of the bets, with the other bet, which pays back itself and the other bet.)
Keep doing that and you'll eventually end up racking up the PAC points, becuase, each spin loses you 25 cents, and you get a PAC point every 40 dollars (and since you win back that 25 cents, you're essentially losing nothing).
Except on 0.
Then you lose fifty cents outright. :P

"C:\Program Files (x86)\mirc\...<etc>" WITH quotes
just do /load -rs gtsdll.ini
why would you even give it the path?
that generally goes to %appdata%\mIRC I find
Well, I needed to; since it was in my other HDD XD
it doesn't on 6.21.
